    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative vehicle, a specimen that defines the standard for automotive excellence. Maintained in pristine, showroom condition, the exterior retains its original luster while the interior remains entirely unblemished. Every mechanical component has been subjected to rigorous inspection to ensure performance that mirrors its factory-new state. For the discerning client who accepts nothing less than the definitive example of the marque, this offering represents an unparalleled acquisition opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
