    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since the moment I got it! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be absolutely obsessed! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
